      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Harlan waves you closer. As you approach, you see that he's holding a scroll of light. You watch as he traces delicate sparkling yellow lines over its surface with a golden stylus."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\u201cThis marvelous device is a mapping system,\" he says. \"As I explore the tunnels, I trace my route through the environment on the scroll. Quisi's doing the same. Once we\u2019ve finished exploring the artery, we'll combine the information in her scroll with mine and create a reasonably accurate three-dimensional map of the entire area that we can reproduce in flowsteel."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\"I was just about to finish up here. Care to help me track down my daughter? She's around here somewhere!\""
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h4",
      "items": [
